{"tid":314610,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得戲院好嘈？","createTime":"2017-07-09T11:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T12:17:54.000Z","uid":7971,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c9d7c7fe1fcaa1a9f301f83a8c9d33ef7aab9e","tid":314610,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始 想搵一間靜少少的戲院<br />\n可以全場靜哂咁睇一場戲 都變得好奢侈<br />\n<br />\n近年的戲院 會見到好多依啲現象<br />\n<br />\n1. 傾計 <br />\n討論劇情 再一邊講一邊笑<br />\n不論咩年紀 小至中學生 大到C9 都會傾<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n有次睇鬼片 週圍女生 將會有少少恐佈<br />\n已經講定好驚 好不安<br />\n然後 後排男女再瘋狂傾計 <br />\n最後開到聲 指住佢問佢地講完尾<br />\n最後都唔會收聲<br />\n<br />\n又試過 前5,6行 成班細佬大聲傾計<br />\n家長旁人都不理 <br />\n<br />\n2. 襟電話<br />\n特別多會係中年人仕 同 港女<br />\n啲呀叔好鐘意一面睇戲 一面襟wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再用speaker播返段錄音都見過<br />\n又或者隔離個港女覺得套戲好悶<br />\n用個過光到仆街的iphone襟IG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多 但傾計講野 已經由唔知幾時開始<br />\n變成一種文化 同只要唔係好大聲 都要包容一樣<br />\n連電影節 電影中心 依啲戲院 電影<br />\n我都遇過上述情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有人講野 我會即場開聲屌<br />\n唔係鍵盤戰士 返到屋企 先屌人"},{"pid":"1d8fa0df7760ce0cf2e7b9c81fe162c00dead2fb","tid":314610,"uid":110005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"Aggar"},{"pid":"eb92368882ce857979375c6fabd0897e9538a997","tid":314610,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"根本D人越來越蝗，有乜計?入左場先大大聲開薯片汽水嘅又一堆，食爆谷食到隔離街都聲到又一堆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faad10e3987baefd86afe4a82013f60f1976538f","tid":314610,"uid":42848,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"覺，好撚煩，而家睇戲真係睇彩數，間間戲院都有啲人渣"},{"pid":"d795578eb3ba74c236822e3eb6636f7b7940121c","tid":314610,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"有次成班小學雞係度劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67a6a63d310069e046b69f1f75a7da07c48c510","tid":314610,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"去嘉湖銀座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e931d0cb04f58efdce144c792b5e02895d90dc5","tid":314610,"uid":48473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"聽錄音真係痴線 心諗出去聽啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaa86b0248326379f65df3ee39c5dce5ffc500d","tid":314610,"uid":7971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去嘉湖銀座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前會覺得市區戲院一開場就好靜<br />\n特別港島區戲院<br />\n然後覺得新界戲院嘈啲<br />\ne.g巴倫紐 元朗 <br />\n<br />\n但依家 全港戲院好都嘈<br />\n仲要唔單單係蝗問題 連香港人都會傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4658d876d1bac12dd3bbc2a5f670f4350751ea","tid":314610,"uid":43480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"試過有個醉酒鬼佬坐前面<br />\n臭到仆街<br />\n仲係咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983ee202b1c73901ceb1322fabacb36557b117ed","tid":314610,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"唔止廢老 中年人後生仔都係咁無品 唔守規矩 無同理心<br />\n制止佢都唔肯停，完全唔知醜"},{"pid":"69dda9a7d3034635a6d128271f12635e7a5bac43","tid":314610,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去嘉湖銀座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前會覺得市區戲院一開場就好靜<br />\n特別港島區戲院<br />\n然後覺得新界戲院嘈啲<br />\ne.g巴倫紐 元朗 <br />\n<br />\n但依家 全港戲院好都嘈<br 